.row.jumbotron.clearfix
  .col-lg-6.col-sm-12.col-md-6.form-group.uploadfile
    h3 Upload CSV Data
    fieldset
      form(action='/uploadfile', method='post', enctype='multipart/form-data')
          input#Collection(name='Collection', type='hidden', value='SampleData')
          label(for='upload',class="control-label") Choose CVS file to upload:
          input(type='file', accept='.csv', name='uploadfile', class="filestyle", data-buttonText='Select a File')
          button(type='submit', name='submit',class="btn btn-primary submitbtn") Upload File
  .col-lg-6.col-sm-12
    h3 How it works?
    ul
      li Download a sample CSV file from our Sample Data Set repository - 
      li Add your data in sample CSV file or create your own. At the moment ROMImate supports only following predefined attributes:
        ul
          li TDate,TV,Radio,Newspaper,Sales
          li Date value in "TDate" field must be in "mm/dd/yyyy" format.
      li Upload your sample data and see media mix modeling result with details of regression models generated from your data.
      li Once you upload your data, You can play with your data in Data Table Section of this interface.
